tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE weather_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    course_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    temperature FLOAT,
    humidity FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE player_scores (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_name TEXT,
    course_id INT,
    round_date DATE,
    score INT
);

CREATE TABLE WeatherData (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    golf_course_id INT,
    date DATE,
    temperature DECIMAL,
    humidity DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE golf_courses (
  course_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  course_name VARCHAR(255),
  location VARCHAR(255),
  par INT
)

CREATE TABLE weather_data (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  course_id INT,
  date DATE,
  temperature FLOAT,
  precipitation FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE player_data (
  player_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  player_name VARCHAR(255),
  handicap FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE tee_times (
  tee_time_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  course_id INT,
  player_id INT,
  date DATE,
  time TIME
)

CREATE TABLE game_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  course_id INT,
  player_id INT,
  date DATE,
  score INT
)
